Instalar
yay -S rofi

Repositorios
1> https://github.com/davatorium/rofi
2> https://github.com/InioX/matugen-themes?tab=readme-ov-file#rofi

Archivos a crear

rofi no genera su archivo config por default, se puede generar ejecutando estos comandos

mkdir -p ~/.config/rofi/themes #crear carpeta para rofi

rofi -dump-config > ~/.config/rofi/config.rasi #crear archivo de config y depositar la config default de rofi

vim ~/.config/rofi/themes/template.rasi #este es el nombre del tema con el cual invocaremos a rofi



/* ==========================================================
   Rofi theme
   Base: gruvbox-light
   Colors: Matugen (Material You)
   ========================================================== */
@import "theme-matugen.rasi"

* {
    /* Text */
    font: "monospace 11";
    highlight: bold italic;

    /* Base colors */
    background:              @surface;
    foreground:              @on-surface;
    bordercolor:             @outline;

    /* Normal */
    normal-background:       @surface;
    normal-foreground:       @on-surface;
    alternate-normal-background: @surface-container;
    alternate-normal-foreground: @on-surface;

    /* Selected */
    selected-normal-background: @primary-container;
    selected-normal-foreground: @on-primary-container;

    /* Active */
    active-background:       @secondary-container;
    active-foreground:       @on-secondary-container;
    alternate-active-background: @surface-container-high;
    alternate-active-foreground: @on-surface;
    selected-active-background:  @secondary;
    selected-active-foreground:  @on-secondary;

    /* Urgent */
    urgent-background:       @error-container;
    urgent-foreground:       @on-error-container;
    alternate-urgent-background: @error-container;
    alternate-urgent-foreground: @on-error-container;
    selected-urgent-background:  @error;
    selected-urgent-foreground:  @on-error;

    /* UI elements */
    separatorcolor:          @outline-variant;
    scrollbar-handle:        @outline;

    /* Window */
    window-background:       @surface-container;
    window-border-color:     @outline;
}

/* ==========================================================
   Layout
   ========================================================== */

window {
    width: 600;
    height: 365;
    background-color: @surface-container;
    border: 2px;
    border-color: @outline;
    padding: 2px;
    border-radius: 10;
}

mainbox {
    background-color: transparent;
    padding: 0px;
    spacing: 0px;
    border: 0px;
    margin: 0px;
}

textbox {
    enabled: false;
}

message {
    enabled: false;
}

separator {
    enabled: false;
}

inputbar {
    enabled: false;
    background-color: @surface-container-high;
    text-color: @on-surface;
    padding: 0px;
    border-radius: 0px;
}

prompt {
    text-color: @primary;
}

entry {
    text-color: @on-surface;
}

listview {
/*mosaico*/
    layout: vertical;
    columns: 3;
    lines: 2;
    spacing: 2px; 
    fixed-height: true;
    background-color: transparent;
    scrollbar: true;
}

element {
    background-color: transparent;
    text-color: @on-surface;
    orientation: vertical;
    flow: vertical;
    padding: 0px;
    margin: 0px;
    spacing: 0px;
    min-height: 190px;
    border-radius: 10px;
}

element normal.normal {
    background-color: @surface;
}

element normal.selected {
    background-color: @primary-container;
    text-color: @on-primary-container;
}

element active.normal {
    background-color: @secondary-container;
    text-color: @on-secondary-container;
}

element urgent.normal {
    background-color: @error-container;
    text-color: @on-error-container;
}

element-text {
/*quitar nombre de imagenes*/
    enabled: false; 
    background-color: transparent;
    text-color: inherit;
}

element-icon {
/*tamano de iconos*/
    size: 175px; 
    background-color: transparent;
    horizontal-align: 0.5;
    vertical-align: 0.5;
}

scrollbar {
    width: 0px;
    handle-width: 0px;
    handle-color: @outline;
    background-color: @surface-container-low;
}



vim ~/.config/matugen/templates/rofi-colors.rasi

hay un template de ejemplo en el repositorio 2, copiar todo el contenido
sugerencia: para hacer rofi transparente agregar el valor hex siguiente al final de cada color:
20% = 33
40% = 66
60% = 99
80% = cc

ejemplo:  
primary: {{colors.primary.default.hex}}cc; #cc es 80%, eso se agregara al valor del color y rofi lo entendera como valor de transparencia para ese color

Modificaciones
vim ~/.config/matugen/config/toml

[templates.rofi]
input_path = "templates/rofi-colors.rasi"
output_path = "~/.config/rofi/themes/<nombre-paleta-rofi>.rasi"

GENERAR PALETA DE MATUGEN 1 VEZ

vim ~/.config/rofi/themes/template.rasi
agregar hasta arriba:
@import = "<nombre-paleta-rofi>.rasi"

